WEBVTT

00:00:01.120 --> 00:00:06.250
I will now outline your
final mission: Operation Skuld.

00:00:06.250 --> 00:00:09.540
You must change the outcome
without altering established past events.

00:00:09.540 --> 00:00:14.580
Okabe Rintaro observes Makise
Kurisu on the ground, soaked in blood.

00:00:14.580 --> 00:00:18.950
You must change the outcome
without altering that established event.

00:00:23.120 --> 00:00:25.620
Hand me that screwdriver, Dad.

00:00:25.620 --> 00:00:30.160
-Why do you keep calling me that?
-Just hurry up.

00:00:30.160 --> 00:00:33.620
Looks like this is it.

00:00:33.620 --> 00:00:37.910
There's only enough fuel left
for one trip to the past and back.

00:00:37.910 --> 00:00:41.830
You mean you can't return to your time?

00:00:41.830 --> 00:00:44.370
I never intended to.

00:00:46.000 --> 00:00:49.160
Changing the world line
here will change the future,

00:00:49.160 --> 00:00:52.160
so I won't need to go back.

00:00:52.160 --> 00:00:54.000
It's just...

00:00:55.370 --> 00:01:01.250
If we don't change things,
then I'll be stuck here for good...

00:01:01.250 --> 00:01:03.910
...living a life of regret.

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:10.500
That's nonsense.

00:01:12.870 --> 00:01:14.330
Uncle...

00:01:14.330 --> 00:01:16.040
Don't call me that.

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:19.290
I am Hououin Kyouma.

00:01:19.290 --> 00:01:21.830
A mad scientist...

00:01:21.830 --> 00:01:25.330
...and the destroyer of
this world's ruling structure.

00:01:25.330 --> 00:01:28.700
Failure is out of the question.

00:01:33.000 --> 00:01:35.700
Okay. I believe in you.

00:01:36.620 --> 00:01:40.120
We will now set Operation Skuld into motion!

00:01:40.120 --> 00:01:41.870
The time has come!

00:01:56.250 --> 00:02:01.450
For you, the assertion of
life and its meaningless proof

00:02:01.450 --> 00:02:08.120
are so comical they don't
even help pass the boredom

00:02:08.120 --> 00:02:13.330
Those of a foolish race,
acting as if they ruled over all,

00:02:13.330 --> 00:02:19.250
presented a conceited, childish theorem

00:02:19.250 --> 00:02:25.370
"Infinite" love and the far reaches of the sky

00:02:25.370 --> 00:02:31.250
are part of a hypothetical
freedom we've been shown

00:02:31.250 --> 00:02:37.450
"Finite" is the merciless march of time,

00:02:37.450 --> 00:02:42.040
leading to a choice to deny even tomorrow

00:02:42.040 --> 00:02:44.290
Hacking to the Gate

00:02:44.290 --> 00:02:51.200
The countless brilliant days
and promises made to my friends...

00:02:51.200 --> 00:02:56.120
I must not "undo" any of it

00:02:56.120 --> 00:03:03.120
So I'll use what tricks I have left to deceive time,

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:09.830
as a lone observer who no longer has doubt

00:03:14.120 --> 00:03:15.000
Where is it?!

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:18.160
I know I put it around here somewhere...

00:03:19.450 --> 00:03:22.080
"The time has come!" you exclaim!

00:03:22.080 --> 00:03:26.160
But then you shamble back to the
lab because you forgot something...

00:03:26.160 --> 00:03:27.870
Hurry up.

00:03:27.870 --> 00:03:32.870
We can't leave the time
machine up there for too long.

00:03:32.870 --> 00:03:35.580
I think this is...

00:03:40.700 --> 00:03:42.950
The Glow Stick Saber?

00:03:42.950 --> 00:03:44.750
What are you gonna do with that?

00:03:44.750 --> 00:03:48.080
The fake blood planted
in the tip is what I need.

00:03:48.080 --> 00:03:50.410
Huh?! I didn't know it had that...

00:03:50.410 --> 00:03:54.950
I see. That's going to serve
as Makise Kurisu's "blood," huh?

00:03:54.950 --> 00:03:56.580
Indeed.

00:03:56.580 --> 00:04:02.500
If the July 28th version of me finds
her unconscious in a pool of fake blood,

00:04:02.500 --> 00:04:04.950
the established past will remain unchanged.

00:04:04.950 --> 00:04:07.870
That's what Operation Skuld is about.

00:04:07.870 --> 00:04:10.830
Well, your idea is sound, but...

00:04:10.830 --> 00:04:12.830
Doesn't that seem too simplistic?

00:04:12.830 --> 00:04:14.870
It felt like the future Okarin

00:04:14.870 --> 00:04:19.750
was talking about
something way more enigmatic...

00:04:20.750 --> 00:04:24.830
Hououin Kyouma is the type
to exaggerate about a plan

00:04:24.830 --> 00:04:27.000
the more simplistic it is.

00:04:28.040 --> 00:04:29.120
Fool.

00:04:29.120 --> 00:04:33.700
I already see through your ways!

00:04:33.700 --> 00:04:36.410
I don't know whether to be impressed or not...

00:04:36.410 --> 00:04:38.000
Sadface.

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:40.830
Say, Okarin.

00:04:42.200 --> 00:04:48.040
Did Kurisu-san used to sit here with you?

00:04:48.040 --> 00:04:49.160
Mayuri...

00:04:49.160 --> 00:04:52.790
She'd always talk a lot with Daru-kun...

00:04:52.790 --> 00:04:57.700
I never understood her,
but she would talk so excitedly...

00:04:57.700 --> 00:05:01.330
She and you would argue all the time,

00:05:01.330 --> 00:05:03.370
but I could tell you were good friends...

00:05:03.370 --> 00:05:05.750
What are you talking about, Mayushii?

00:05:05.750 --> 00:05:08.700
Makise Kurisu is a scientific genius.

00:05:08.700 --> 00:05:11.000
She'd never come to a lab like this.

00:05:11.000 --> 00:05:13.830
You're right. That'd be strange.

00:05:13.830 --> 00:05:16.790
Maybe I just dreamed it...

00:05:16.790 --> 00:05:19.540
Could it be she has the Reading Steiner too?

00:05:19.540 --> 00:05:23.290
No, there's no such ability.

00:05:23.290 --> 00:05:26.830
But... some part inside remembers

00:05:26.830 --> 00:05:29.540
what's happened in other world lines...

00:05:29.540 --> 00:05:32.830
Everyone remembers, somewhere deep down...

00:05:32.830 --> 00:05:36.450
Kurisu did everything she could to save Mayuri.

00:05:36.450 --> 00:05:41.790
It's because of Kurisu that
Mayuri--no, that we're-here now.

00:05:41.790 --> 00:05:43.410
Huh?

00:05:44.790 --> 00:05:46.750
Say, Okarin.

00:05:46.750 --> 00:05:49.790
Do you like Kurisu-san?

00:05:52.750 --> 00:05:55.330
Christina is my assistant...

00:05:55.330 --> 00:05:57.200
...a dear friend...

00:05:57.200 --> 00:06:00.200
...and someone special to me.

00:06:01.080 --> 00:06:03.040
Ah!

00:06:03.040 --> 00:06:05.870
And she's also in love with me.

00:06:05.870 --> 00:06:08.950
No way! This is so real-life...

00:06:08.950 --> 00:06:13.830
Then you definitely have
to save her. No matter what.

00:06:16.370 --> 00:06:18.500
You have to save her!

00:06:20.120 --> 00:06:21.750
Yeah...

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:34.540
Promise you'll come
back, okay? With Kurisu-san...

00:06:34.540 --> 00:06:35.540
But of course.

00:06:35.540 --> 00:06:37.120
U-Umm...

00:06:37.120 --> 00:06:39.540
Miss Amane...

00:06:39.540 --> 00:06:42.790
If you really are my daughter...

00:06:42.790 --> 00:06:44.700
...then who's my wife?

00:06:46.450 --> 00:06:48.200
I'll leave that a secret.

00:06:48.200 --> 00:06:50.040
Again?

00:06:51.250 --> 00:06:52.870
Let's go!

00:07:07.700 --> 00:07:10.540
I've brought us to the
exact same time as before.

00:07:10.540 --> 00:07:12.370
The rest is up to you.

00:07:12.370 --> 00:07:13.620
I know.

00:07:13.620 --> 00:07:16.120
Leave the Glow Stick Saber at the spot for me.

00:07:16.120 --> 00:07:17.660
No problem.

00:07:19.410 --> 00:07:23.660
Changing the outcome without
altering the established past...

00:07:23.660 --> 00:07:25.790
The first order of business...

00:07:27.120 --> 00:07:29.080
...is this.

00:07:29.080 --> 00:07:30.950
I don't know how it connects to all this.

00:07:30.950 --> 00:07:35.120
But if I get the Metal Oopa now,

00:07:35.120 --> 00:07:40.120
it'll reduce the chance of
metal getting into that envelope.

00:07:45.080 --> 00:07:46.830
Just as I thought.

00:07:52.660 --> 00:07:55.080
There aren't many in this series left,

00:07:55.080 --> 00:07:59.870
but Mayushii's out of 100-yen coins...

00:07:59.870 --> 00:08:02.040
Don't act so spoiled, Mayuri.

00:08:02.040 --> 00:08:04.950
Even if we are childhood friends,
I'm not lending you money.

00:08:04.950 --> 00:08:07.330
Aww...

00:08:07.330 --> 00:08:12.000
Allow me to show you
the harsh realities of life.

00:08:19.410 --> 00:08:21.120
It's an Oopa!

00:08:21.120 --> 00:08:22.540
Is it rare?

00:08:22.540 --> 00:08:27.200
No, but it's really cute, don't you think?

00:08:27.200 --> 00:08:29.450
Okay. Next up...!

00:08:38.080 --> 00:08:39.450
Oh, pardon me--

00:08:39.450 --> 00:08:42.080
K-Kurisu...

00:08:42.080 --> 00:08:45.370
Huh? How do you know my name?

00:08:47.120 --> 00:08:49.580
Have we met before?

00:08:49.580 --> 00:08:50.750
Kurisu...

00:08:50.750 --> 00:08:52.250
Are you even listening--

00:08:54.250 --> 00:08:56.250
What's your problem?!

00:08:56.250 --> 00:08:58.370
Answer my question!

00:08:59.160 --> 00:09:00.790
I'm...

00:09:03.000 --> 00:09:07.250
I'm here... to save you.

00:09:08.040 --> 00:09:14.040
Dr. Nakabachi's conference is
about to begin in the 8th floor hall.

00:09:14.040 --> 00:09:16.790
Wait! Stop!

00:09:26.620 --> 00:09:31.660
I never thought I'd have
to pretend to be myself...

00:09:42.040 --> 00:09:46.250
So Kurisu picked up the
Oopa after Mayuri dropped it...!

00:09:46.250 --> 00:09:49.700
But since this one isn't metal,

00:09:49.700 --> 00:09:55.080
Nakabachi's envelope should
burn up in the airplane accident now.

00:10:02.870 --> 00:10:06.250
Now I just need to drive Nakabachi away

00:10:06.250 --> 00:10:10.250
and find a chance to knock Kurisu out...

00:10:21.620 --> 00:10:24.160
The fake blood's dried up?!

00:10:25.080 --> 00:10:26.540
I see...

00:10:26.540 --> 00:10:32.450
It was left unused for so long
that the air exposure solidified it...

00:10:32.450 --> 00:10:35.160
-What do you want?
-Umm, I'd like you to read...

00:10:35.160 --> 00:10:37.870
-Think... Think!
-Umm, I'd like you to read...

00:10:37.870 --> 00:10:39.830
There's gotta be something!

00:10:39.830 --> 00:10:41.500
Something...!

00:10:42.290 --> 00:10:44.660
Think.

00:10:44.660 --> 00:10:48.580
Getting rid of Nakabachi
should be easy enough.

00:10:48.580 --> 00:10:50.950
The problem is the blood.

00:10:50.950 --> 00:10:53.200
I just need something
else that looks like blood!

00:10:53.200 --> 00:10:54.790
Be quiet!

00:10:56.620 --> 00:10:58.580
How dare you call me a thief...!

00:10:58.580 --> 00:11:00.290
That's it!

00:11:03.000 --> 00:11:05.000
Stop it!

00:11:05.000 --> 00:11:06.700
Who the hell are you?!

00:11:08.500 --> 00:11:13.330
I am the seeker of chaos, the destroyer
of this world's ruling structure...

00:11:13.330 --> 00:11:15.080
...and...

00:11:15.080 --> 00:11:17.750
...the shatterer of your ambitions!

00:11:19.040 --> 00:11:22.120
Do you wish to hear it?

00:11:22.120 --> 00:11:23.910
My name is...

00:11:25.160 --> 00:11:27.000
...Hououin...

00:11:27.540 --> 00:11:29.410
...Kyouma!

00:11:30.410 --> 00:11:33.540
What nonsense is this?

00:11:33.540 --> 00:11:36.540
You're that kid...!

00:11:36.540 --> 00:11:41.080
I see. So that's how it is...

00:11:41.080 --> 00:11:47.040
The two of you conspired
to ruin my press conference.

00:11:49.160 --> 00:11:52.200
Now I see. So that's how it is...

00:11:55.450 --> 00:11:57.620
Daddy...!

00:11:57.620 --> 00:12:00.160
-Run!
-I refuse!

00:12:00.160 --> 00:12:05.250
What's wrong? What's the knife for?

00:12:05.250 --> 00:12:07.370
Wh-What?!

00:12:07.370 --> 00:12:09.660
Just acting tough?

00:12:09.660 --> 00:12:14.290
Afraid of my god-like power, are you?

00:12:15.080 --> 00:12:16.540
L-Like hell I am!

00:12:16.540 --> 00:12:18.620
What's the matter?!

00:12:18.620 --> 00:12:20.950
You're shaking. Are you scared?

00:12:20.950 --> 00:12:24.250
How long are you going to mock me?!

00:12:24.250 --> 00:12:28.250
In the end, you're just a pathetic little man.

00:12:28.250 --> 00:12:31.540
If you can't even appreciate
your own daughter's abilities...

00:12:31.540 --> 00:12:35.040
...then you could never kill me!

00:12:35.040 --> 00:12:36.660
Never...!

00:12:36.660 --> 00:12:38.410
Never!

00:12:46.870 --> 00:12:48.500
N-No...

00:13:01.540 --> 00:13:05.160
N-No... This can't be...

00:13:06.370 --> 00:13:08.830
Th-That'll teach you...!

00:13:08.830 --> 00:13:14.290
-Stay calm... Just a little more...
-Th-That's what you get for mocking me...

00:13:28.540 --> 00:13:33.250
H-How dare you...

00:13:33.250 --> 00:13:36.500
I'll kill...

00:13:36.500 --> 00:13:39.080
I'll kill you...!

00:13:48.040 --> 00:13:50.660
I'll get you for this!

00:14:00.660 --> 00:14:03.370
D-Don't move!

00:14:03.370 --> 00:14:07.250
L-Lie down! I'll call an ambulance!

00:14:09.790 --> 00:14:12.000
Hello?! Emergency services?!

00:14:12.000 --> 00:14:13.580
Come right away!

00:14:13.580 --> 00:14:15.750
-Someone's been stabbed!
-I...

00:14:18.290 --> 00:14:20.750
...told you...

00:14:22.290 --> 00:14:24.870
...I would...

00:14:24.870 --> 00:14:26.660
...save you...!

00:15:17.910 --> 00:15:19.660
This is...

00:15:19.660 --> 00:15:23.450
...without a doubt...

00:15:23.450 --> 00:15:25.200
...the Kurisu I saw.

00:15:34.290 --> 00:15:35.910
Uncle...

00:15:44.080 --> 00:15:45.700
Goodbye...

00:15:48.870 --> 00:15:50.790
-Wait...
-Huh?

00:15:53.500 --> 00:15:56.750
Just hold on a minute...

00:15:56.750 --> 00:15:59.370
This is no time for that!

00:15:59.370 --> 00:16:01.330
If we don't hurry, you'll...!

00:16:01.330 --> 00:16:02.950
Please...

00:16:11.370 --> 00:16:12.500
Hey.

00:16:12.500 --> 00:16:14.660
Is someone there...?

00:16:14.660 --> 00:16:16.500
Good luck.

00:16:16.500 --> 00:16:18.620
You're about to begin...

00:16:18.620 --> 00:16:22.000
...the longest and most important...

00:16:22.000 --> 00:16:25.370
...three weeks of your life.

00:16:35.500 --> 00:16:40.330
That was too reckless!
Just how stupid are you?!

00:16:40.330 --> 00:16:43.450
What do you mean, stupid?
The plan worked, didn't it...?

00:16:43.450 --> 00:16:45.620
I've only superficially stopped the bleeding.

00:16:45.620 --> 00:16:47.750
Go straight to the hospital when you get back.

00:16:47.750 --> 00:16:50.500
It'll be tough, but stay strong.

00:16:50.500 --> 00:16:51.950
Here we go!

00:17:04.950 --> 00:17:06.700
Is this...?

00:17:08.750 --> 00:17:11.950
Steins Gate is a world line unknown to all.

00:17:11.950 --> 00:17:13.370
Suzuha...

00:17:14.200 --> 00:17:19.330
But if your theory is correct,
that paper will burn up,

00:17:19.330 --> 00:17:21.910
the time machine development
race will never happen,

00:17:21.910 --> 00:17:26.160
and World War III will never take place.

00:17:26.160 --> 00:17:29.330
I can't stay with you.

00:17:29.330 --> 00:17:32.750
So I'll thank you while I can.

00:17:35.330 --> 00:17:36.950
Thanks.

00:17:38.830 --> 00:17:42.160
See you again, in seven years...

00:17:52.120 --> 00:17:58.080
"For Okarin Okabe Rintaro"

00:17:58.080 --> 00:18:00.040
"Okabe Rintaro"

00:18:00.620 --> 00:18:02.620
Okarin!

00:18:03.450 --> 00:18:05.080
Huh?

00:18:07.080 --> 00:18:12.700
That paper on time machines
was the key to mankind's future!

00:18:12.700 --> 00:18:14.410
But it burned up!

00:18:14.410 --> 00:18:15.910
His comments are incoherent,

00:18:15.910 --> 00:18:19.370
and the Russian government
is poised to deny his defection--

00:18:19.370 --> 00:18:22.540
Ruka-kun! Okarin was here?!

00:18:22.540 --> 00:18:24.790
I must've just missed him...

00:18:24.790 --> 00:18:26.450
Oh, when he was here...

00:18:28.250 --> 00:18:31.620
It identifies you as Lab Member 006.

00:18:31.620 --> 00:18:34.540
Huh? When did I become a lab member?

00:18:34.540 --> 00:18:40.200
Perhaps those memories
reside in a previous life.

00:18:40.200 --> 00:18:42.580
Oh?

00:18:42.580 --> 00:18:45.000
I wonder what these letters are...

00:18:45.000 --> 00:18:46.410
Kyouma?

00:18:46.410 --> 00:18:48.500
He was just here, meow!

00:18:48.500 --> 00:18:50.200
He was?

00:18:50.200 --> 00:18:53.620
Did he give you anything, Faris-chan?

00:18:53.620 --> 00:18:55.750
Actually...

00:18:55.750 --> 00:18:59.660
It's a badge for Lab Member 007.

00:18:59.660 --> 00:19:02.950
If you ever need help, hold it tight

00:19:02.950 --> 00:19:06.330
and chant, "La Yoda Stasella!"

00:19:06.330 --> 00:19:08.000
Oh...

00:19:09.500 --> 00:19:13.330
Huh? If you're lookin'
for Okabe, he was just here.

00:19:13.330 --> 00:19:14.450
Big Sis Mayuri!

00:19:14.450 --> 00:19:16.250
Too-too-roo, Nae-chan!

00:19:16.250 --> 00:19:17.700
-And...?
-Ah!

00:19:17.700 --> 00:19:20.790
This is our new part-timer as of today!

00:19:20.790 --> 00:19:22.790
I'm Kiryu Moeka...

00:19:22.790 --> 00:19:25.500
She helped Nae after she took a spill.

00:19:25.500 --> 00:19:30.410
She said she didn't have a job,
so I brought her on board.

00:19:30.410 --> 00:19:32.500
I'm Shiina Mayuri!

00:19:34.620 --> 00:19:36.450
She sure is popular.

00:19:36.450 --> 00:19:40.660
Ol' Okabe started hitting
on her as soon as they met...

00:19:40.660 --> 00:19:44.540
Visit our lab anytime you want.

00:19:46.080 --> 00:19:47.700
Umm...

00:19:48.830 --> 00:19:50.500
Thank you...

00:19:54.120 --> 00:19:55.830
Too-too-roo!

00:19:55.830 --> 00:19:57.750
Welcome back-arin!

00:19:57.750 --> 00:20:00.950
Did you combine "Welcome back" and "Okarin"?

00:20:00.950 --> 00:20:02.750
Yeah!

00:20:02.750 --> 00:20:03.830
Where's Okarin?

00:20:03.830 --> 00:20:06.540
Oh, he went to buy some things.

00:20:06.540 --> 00:20:08.120
Oh...

00:20:08.120 --> 00:20:10.080
Oh!

00:20:10.080 --> 00:20:13.580
These? He says they're lab member badges.

00:20:13.580 --> 00:20:17.500
Lab Member 002 and 003!

00:20:17.500 --> 00:20:20.330
When did we gain so many members, though?

00:20:20.330 --> 00:20:23.660
He said they go all the way up to 008...

00:20:23.660 --> 00:20:25.250
There's "O" for Okarin...

00:20:25.250 --> 00:20:29.200
Shiina, Hashida, Urushibara, Faris...

00:20:29.200 --> 00:20:32.540
Huh? What do M, K, and A stand for?

00:20:32.540 --> 00:20:33.950
Beats me.

00:20:33.950 --> 00:20:38.410
He also put one in a box.

00:20:38.410 --> 00:20:42.870
Lab Member 008 will
appear seven years from now.

00:20:42.870 --> 00:20:44.700
More of your delusions?

00:20:44.700 --> 00:20:47.200
It's an inevitability. For you.

00:20:47.200 --> 00:20:48.830
Me...?

00:20:50.000 --> 00:20:52.290
Seven years from now...

00:20:52.290 --> 00:20:56.040
I can't wait! I wonder
what that person will be like!

00:20:56.040 --> 00:21:00.160
I can't even imagine that far ahead...

00:21:00.160 --> 00:21:04.870
I don't think the lab will ever change, though.

00:21:04.870 --> 00:21:08.450
No matter how much time passes...

00:21:10.250 --> 00:21:13.410
Where are you now?

00:21:13.410 --> 00:21:17.500
Are you working on a paper at
an American research institute?

00:21:17.500 --> 00:21:22.540
Are you pulling an all-nighter on
an experiment to test an idea of yours?

00:21:22.540 --> 00:21:27.160
Maybe you're still troubled by
what happened with your father.

00:21:28.250 --> 00:21:32.750
You have no memory of the
three weeks you spent with me.

00:21:32.750 --> 00:21:34.330
But that's okay.

00:21:34.330 --> 00:21:35.910
Somewhere out there

00:21:35.910 --> 00:21:41.200
you're breathing, speaking,
thinking hard about something...

00:21:41.200 --> 00:21:43.910
That's all that matters.

00:21:43.910 --> 00:21:48.330
Because somewhere out there
you're looking at the same world I am...

00:21:48.330 --> 00:21:51.410
...this world with an unknown future.

00:22:06.200 --> 00:22:09.830
I... finally found you...

00:22:12.450 --> 00:22:14.910
I've been looking everywhere for you.

00:22:15.580 --> 00:22:18.870
I wanted to thank you for saving me...

00:22:27.750 --> 00:22:29.500
It's me.

00:22:29.500 --> 00:22:32.250
What is she doing here?

00:22:33.040 --> 00:22:36.540
What? You want me to protect her?

00:22:36.540 --> 00:22:40.410
Sheesh. Talk about an indulgent order.

00:22:40.410 --> 00:22:42.410
But no matter.

00:22:42.410 --> 00:22:45.200
If that's its choice...

00:22:45.200 --> 00:22:47.620
El Psy Congroo.

00:22:47.620 --> 00:22:49.540
"Elp Sy"...?

00:22:50.870 --> 00:22:52.750
We meet again, Christina!

00:22:52.750 --> 00:22:57.160
I told you, I'm not
"Christina" or your assistant!

00:22:57.160 --> 00:22:58.790
Huh?

00:23:03.040 --> 00:23:06.040
Welcome, assistant of mine...

00:23:06.040 --> 00:23:07.160
...Makise Kurisu.

00:23:07.160 --> 00:23:10.200
No, Christina.

00:23:12.660 --> 00:23:17.950
No one knows what the future holds.

00:23:17.950 --> 00:23:24.200
That's precisely why, just as
this reunion demonstrates...

00:23:24.200 --> 00:23:26.450
...the possibilities are infinite.

00:23:28.950 --> 00:23:33.660
This is the choice of Steins Gate.

